				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\hbox {C/O}\,<\,1$$\end{document} by number), C-CSEs (carbon stars, C/O>1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
